---
description: Frontend rules
globs: frontend/**
---

Use React + Vite + TypeScript.

Use CSS Modules for component styles.
Each styled component should have its own `*.module.css` file.

Use React Hook Form + Zod for forms and validation.
Do not use Formik.

Keep API calls in a separate service layer.

Keep components small, typed and readable.

Do not implement final visual design yet unless explicitly requested.
